    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "I see what you&#39;re saying, but by that rationale, the same applies to the use of <code>@param</code> for method parameters. Sun&#39;s coding standards explicitly say that <code>@param</code> should be used even if the method parameter&#39;s meaning is clear."
