    "body" : "The <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/13/docs/specs/javadoc/doc-comment-spec.html#param\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">documentation of @param</a> gives instructions for type parameters. Mind you, Oracle could do a better job of advertising this document."
